title: Bloomberg Markets 12/19/2025
description: "Bloomberg Markets" follows the market moves across every global asset class and discusses the biggest issues for Wall Street. Today's guests: Telsey Advisory Group CEO, Chief Research Officer Dana Telsey, Bloomberg's Caroline Hyde, James Seyffart, Nishant Kumar and Ira Boudway.  (Source: Bloomberg)
